span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_17gk'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17gk'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_17gk')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_17gk" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>"People are not base animals, but people, about 90% animal and 10% something new and different. Religion can be looked on as an act of rebellion by the 90% animal against the 10% new and different (most often within the same person)."</p>

