ctober 2009 08:57:17AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17kt'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_17kt')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_17kt" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_17kt" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RichardKennaway/">RichardKennaway</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">27 October 2009 08:57:17AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_17kt'>2 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17kt'] = ['1 point', '2 points', '3 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_17kt')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_17kt" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Quotes are selected for their penetrating insight and importance. Comments, not necessarily.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_17kt"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_17kt" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_17kt')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_17kt" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_17kt')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_17kt" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/17kt?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_17kt" href="#17ff" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_17kt" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_17kt')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_17kt class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_17kt" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_17j8" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_17j8" class="parent"><a name="17j8" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_17j8" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_17j8" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_17j8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/DaveInNYC/">DaveInNYC</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">26 October 2009 11:52:58PM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17j8'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_17j8')">[+] (5 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_17j8" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_17j8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/DaveInNYC/">DaveInNYC</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">26 October 2009 11:52:58PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_17j8'>4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17j8'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_17j8')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_17j8" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>I suspect it is because the main post refers to quotes being "voted up/down separately," i.e. it puts it in people's minds that they are <em>supposed</em> to vote on the quotes. I do find it funny that I got 12 karma points for cutting/pasting a quote; C.S. Lewis deserves the karma points, not me (as evidenced by the fact that I have gotten a grand total of 1 point from my own original posts). If one wanted to game the karma system, posting pithy quotes is the way to go.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_17j8"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_17j8" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_17j8')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_17j8" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_17j8')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_17j8" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/17j8?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_17j8" href="#17ff" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_17j8" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_17j8')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_17j8 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_17j8" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_17j8" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_17j8" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_17je" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_17je" class="parent"><a name="17je" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_17je" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_17je" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_17je" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">27 October 2009 12:23:04AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17je'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_17je')">[+] (4 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_17je" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_17je" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/wedrifid/">wedrifid</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">27 October 2009 12:23:04AM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_17je'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_17je'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_17je')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_17je" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
