thor"><a id="author_t1_173g" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/RobinZ/">RobinZ</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 04:46:10PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_173g'>28 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_173g'] = ['27 points', '28 points', '29 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_173g')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_173g" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
