</span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">23 October 2009 04:45:55AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_177d'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_177d'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_177d')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_177d" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>It's easy to trisect an angle. Just use a protractor. ;)</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_177d"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_177d" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_177d')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_177d" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_177d')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_177d" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/177d?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_177d" href="#1747" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_177d" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_177d')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_177d class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_177d" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1758" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1758" class="parent"><a name="1758" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1758" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1758" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1758" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/SilasBarta/">SilasBarta</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 09:03:17PM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1758'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1758')">[+] (20 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1758" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1758" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/SilasBarta/">SilasBarta</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 09:03:17PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1758'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1758'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1758')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1758" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>What's even worse is trying to get that message to happen.</p>

