<p>-- Esa Lappi, my high school math teacher when showing us the proof of some theorem.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_176i"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_176i" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_176i')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_176i" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_176i')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_176i" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/176i?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_176i" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_176i')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_176i class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_176i" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_176i" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_176i" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1771" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1771" class="parent"><a name="1771" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1771" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1771" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1771" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/randallsquared/">randallsquared</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">23 October 2009 02:57:27AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1771'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1771')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1771" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1771" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/randallsquared/">randallsquared</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">23 October 2009 02:57:27AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1771'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1771'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 p