<p>-- <a href="http://matt-arnold.livejournal.com/294062.html" rel="nofollow">Matt Arnold</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1738"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1738" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1738')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1738" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1738')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1738" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/1738?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1738" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1738')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1738 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1738" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1738" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1738" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_173x" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_173x" class="parent"><a name="173x" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_173x" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_173x" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_173x" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Douglas_Knight/">Douglas_Knight</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 06:13:31PM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_173x'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_173x')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_173x" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_173x" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Douglas_Knight/">Douglas_Knight</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 06:13:31PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_173x'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_173x'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_173x')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_173x" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>I would have been able to read that sentence correctly without context if it had a comma: "allowed to fail, to teach them a lesson."</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_173x"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_173x" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_173x')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_173x" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_173x')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_173x" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/1co/rationality_quotes_october_2009/173x?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_173x" href="#1738" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_173x" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_173x')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_173x class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_173x" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1731" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1731" class="parent"><a name="1731" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1731" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1731" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1731" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Eliezer_Yudkowsky/">Eliezer_Yudkowsky</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 04:11:55PM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1731'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1731')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1731" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1731" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Eliezer_Yudkowsky/">Eliezer_Yudkowsky</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">22 October 2009 04:11:55PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1731'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1731'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1731')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1731" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
